j)

The transformation in question is \(f(\bf{x}) = \frac{\bf{x}-\overline{x}}{Var(\bf{x})}+\overline{x}\) where \(\overline{x}\) is the vector where all entries are the mean of the vector x.

ddn <- t(t(dds)+apply(dd, MARGIN=2, FUN=mean))
